library('psych')

CBB_split <- initial_split(CBB_variables, prop = .75)
CBB_train <- training(CBB_split)
CBB_test <- testing(CBB_split)

CBB_ridge <- cv.glmnet(W ~ ADJOE + ADJDE + EFG_O + EFG_D + TOR + TORD + FTR + FTRD + TEAM + YR,
                       data = CBB_train,
                       # note alpha = 0 sets ridge!  
                       alpha = 0)

REGRESSION TREE

CBB_data <- read_csv("CBB_cleaned.csv")
CBB_variables <- CBB_data %>% select(WINPER, ADJOE, ADJDE, EFG_O, EFG_D, TOR, TORD, FTR, FTRD, TEAM, YR)

CBB_Defense_Tree <- ctree(WINPER ~ ADJDE + EFG_D + TORD +FTRD,
                      data = CBB_variables,
                      control = partykit::ctree_control(alpha= 0.1,
                                                        minbucket = 128))
plot(CBB_Defense_Tree)


CBB_Offense <- ctree(WINPER ~ ADJOE + EFG_O + TOR + FTR,
                     data = CBB_variables,
                     control = partykit::ctree_control(alpha= 0.1,
                                                        minbucket = 128))
plot(CBB_Offense)
